---
title: Cajun Spiced Cheese Tortillas with roast potatoes and sweet chilli sauce
description: Fried to perfection and coated in a smoky cajun spice mix, golden grilling cheese is the star of this recipe. These tortillas are also topped with a tart salad and tender slightly sweet pepper. All accompanied by the perenially popular potato.
